creator: magnus.martensson@karolinska.se
text:
When trying to start apache2 with httpd I get the following error message:

Starting httpd2 (prefork) /usr/sbin/httpd2-prefork: symbol lookup error: /usr/sbin/httpd2-prefork: undefined symbol: apr_bucket_setaside_notimpl

The command line was:
/usr/sbin/httpd2-prefork -f /etc/apache2/httpd.conf
This looks like a distribution specific issue. Please contact your Linux vendor.
creator: rpluem@apache.org
